---
title: Creamy Chicken & Red Pesto Farfalle with Herby Pangrattato & Apple Salad
description: Tonight, cosy up to this creamy, comforting bowl of bow tie pasta loaded with succulent chicken, garlic, crunchy pangrattato and
our moreish red pesto made of sun-dried tomato. We've even added a crisp salad to "tie" it all together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-creamy-red-pesto-farfalle-21638c3d.jpg
